@startuml
title Backend Observability (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

node "Backend FastAPI :8001\n(ENABLE_METRICS=True)" as BE
node "Prometheus :9090" as Prom
node "Grafana :3001" as Gra
node "Promtail" as Pt
node "Loki :3100" as Loki
folder "test1/backend/logs/*.log" as BELogs

BE --> Prom : scrape /metrics\nfreshfood_http_*\nfreshfood_scan_events_total
BELogs --> Pt : tail files
Pt --> Loki : push logs

Gra --> Prom : query metrics
Gra --> Loki : query logs

note right of Prom
Scrape target:
host.docker.internal:8001
metrics_path: /metrics
end note

note right of BELogs
As-is gap:
Promtail da cau hinh doc log file,\nnhung app chua thay logger file ro rang.
end note

@enduml
